  <datafield tag="245" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">Mean <math altimg="si1.gif" display="inline" overflow="scroll"><msub><mrow><mi>p</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi></mrow></msub></math> scaling with <math altimg="si2.gif" display="inline" overflow="scroll"><mi>m</mi><mo stretchy="false">/</mo><msub><mrow><mi>n</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">q</mi></mrow></msub></math> at the LHC: Absence of (hydro) flow in small systems?</subfield>
  </datafield>
